<p xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">Vincent wishes Theo a happy birthday (<ref target="#l-1*">ll. 1*-2</ref>). On the assumption that the letter was supposed to arrive in Paris on 1 May, we have dated it Wednesday, 30 April 1884.</p>
